      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "And when the angel stretched out his hand upon Jerusalem to destroy it, the LORD repented him of the evil, and said to the angel that destroyed the people, It is enough: {i} stay now thine hand. And the angel of the LORD was by the threshingplace of Araunah the Jebusite.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And when the angel stretched out his hand upon Jerusalem to destroy it, the LORD repented him of the evil, and said to the angel that destroyed the people, It is enough: ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{i}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " stay now thine hand. And the angel of the LORD was by the threshingplace of Araunah the Jebusite.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(i) The Lord spared this place, because he had chosen it to build his temple there.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
